<div class="contextual-help-item principal-help"  i18n:domain="novaideo">
    <p i18n:translate="">
        Ideas that have been examined are visible by all users.
    </p>
    <span tal:omit-tag="" tal:condition="'favorable' in context.state">
        <p i18n:translate="" >
            The Examination Committee expressed a positive opinion on this idea. Consequently, it can be transformed into a proposal or used in existing proposals by the members of the platform.
        </p>
         <p i18n:translate="">
            Ideas that were examined and received a positive opinion can be duplicated so that a copy be worked upon differently and you can add them to your favourites.
        </p>
    </span>
    <span tal:omit-tag="" tal:condition="'unfavorable' in context.state">
        <p i18n:translate="" >
            The Examination Committee expressed a negative opinion on this idea. Consequently, it cannot be transformed into a proposal or used in existing proposals by the members of the platform.
        </p>
        <p i18n:translate="">
            Examined ideas, even after having received a negative opinion, can still be duplicated so that a copy be worked upon differently, and you can add them to your favourites.
        </p>
    </span>
    <p i18n:translate="">
        They can also be communicated to third parties or discussed among members.
    </p>
</div>


